%B0-1-%E6%8B%8D%E7%83%82%E7%89%87%E6%AF%94%E6%8B%8D%E5%A5%BD%E7%89%87%E6%9B%B4%E8%B5%9A%E9%92%B1"><span class="nav-number">1.2.2.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">💰 1. 拍烂片比拍好片更赚钱</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%F0%9F%8C%AA%EF%B8%8F-2-%E6%B5%81%E9%87%8F%E6%98%8E%E6%98%9F%E6%8B%96%E5%9E%AE%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E8%A1%A8%E7%8E%B0"><span class="nav-number">1.2.2.2.</span> <span class="nav-text">🌪️ 2. 流量明星拖垮整体表现</span></a></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-4"><a class="nav-link" href="#%E2%9C%82%EF%B8%8F-3-%E7%BC%96%E5%89%A7%E5%88%9B%E4%BD%9C%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%B8%A5%E9%87%8D%E5%8F%97%E9%99%90"><span class="nav-number">1.2.2.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">✂️ 3. 编剧创作空间严重受限</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="nav-item nav-level-2"><a class="nav-link" href="#%F0%9F%8E%9E%EF%B8%8F-%E4%B8%89%E3%80%81%E8%80%81%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%A3%E7%94%B5%E5%BD%B1%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E6%B6%88%E9%80%9D"><span class="nav-number">1.3.</span> <span class="nav-text">🎞️ 三、老一代电影人的消逝</span></a><ol class="nav-child"><li class="nav-item nav-level-3"><a class="nav-link" href="#%F0%9F%A7%B7-%E6%8A%95%E8%B5%84%E6%96%B9%E5%B9%B2%E9%A2%84%E4%B9%9F%E6%98%AF%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98"><span class="nav-number">1.3.1.</span> <span class="nav-text">🧷 投资方干预也是问题</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol></div>
